{
  "stem": "15396.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I spent a few nights, till late at night, sitting in a bar telling him all these various stories about people I'd known during the war, and getting a lot of money for it, and eating awfully well, and sleeping in the Hotel [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I went to Spain where it was warm and all, and didn't have to pay very much.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got much better then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I came back-- and then one day, I was walking in the-- I went in Fouquet's on the Champs Elysees really and truly just out of old time's sake.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By now, I still looked pretty awful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I ran into an old friend of mine, [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Alan Bernheim, ?] who had known me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We'd known each other in Marseille.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had helped us a little bit, you know, and was a very interesting man.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Had a fascinating mother and all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said, oh, I know somebody making a film about Marseille, and you could probably get a job as technical advisor on the [INAUDIBLE] there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I went to Jean [INAUDIBLE], who was making this film, and sure enough, he hired me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then one day we were filming on a tramp steamer that they had rented just for the day, because it had to leave for a run that night.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the sun was going down on the buildings, and the higher paid help, the director, and the producer, and the camera man, and everybody over in a corner, worried.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It seemed that the actor they had brought down to play the captain of the ship was on their way to the hospital to have his appendix out, and they had to establish the fact that they were in that section of Marseille.",
      "word_count": 43
    }
  ],
